# Contact form emails (optional fallback). Prefer **Site config** in Strapi Admin (SMTP host, port, user, password, From).
# When Site config fields are empty, these env vars are used instead.
# SMTP_HOST=
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_SECURE=false
# SMTP_USERNAME=
# SMTP_PASSWORD=
# EMAIL_FROM=noreply@yourdomain.com

# Report Check — lab staff upload uses Strapi **Users & Permissions** (role type `lab-staff`) and JWT, not env secrets.

# Demo / mock content: configured only in the **frontend** `.env` as `VITE_MOCK_DATA` (Vite SPA). There is no mock-data flag for Strapi itself.
